cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CV 

This paper is focused on natural language processing (NLP) and machine learning techniques for language-independent models. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also discusses the use of multilingual representations and data resources, which suggests that it could also fit into the categories of cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of sequence labeling, which is a common task in computer vision, suggesting that it could also fit into the category of cs.CV (Computer Vision).
